flowchart TB
    Client([Client])
    Feed[Feed Service<br/>geo + filter + ML rank]
    Swipe[Swipe Service<br/>record + reciprocity check]
    Match[Match Service]
    Chat[Chat Service]
    Users[(Users + Geo Index)]
    Swipes[(Swipes Store)]
    Bloom[(Swiped Bloom Filter<br/>per-user cache)]

    Client -->|request feed| Feed
    Feed --> Users
    Feed -->|exclude swiped| Bloom
    Feed -.->|candidates| Client
    Client -->|swipe| Swipe
    Swipe --> Swipes
    Swipe -->|reciprocal?| Match
    Match -.->|notify both| Client
    Match --> Chat

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Feed,Swipe,Match,Chat service
    class Users,Swipes,Bloom store
